-5pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>1</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）前端使用<span>jQuery-EasyUI </span>和<span>Ztree</span>框架编写 ，大量使用了<span>Ajax</span>异步请求方式和局部刷新功能</span><span style=\"color:blue;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">，</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">提高了</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-5pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">用户的感官体验。在开发过程中<span>,</span>对于页面我们使用了<span>freemaker</span>模板技术进行了优化。在页面布局上， </span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-5pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">我们使用了<span>jQuery-EasyUI</span>的<span>layout</span>布局，还有使用了大量的<span>jQuery-EasyUI</span>控件使前端页面比较美观。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-5pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>2</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">通用</span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:9pt;\"><span>DAO</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">组件的设计，</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">使用反射和泛型技术，实现增删改查，减少了重复代码，优化了性能。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;font-size:10pt;\"><span>2、</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">基础设置：该模块包括基础档案设置、资费标准、取派员设置、区域设置、管理分区、管理定区六个功能。</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;font-size:10pt;\"> </span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n						<span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">1</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）资费标准、取派员设置、区域设置、管理分区使用了<span>Ajax</span>方式实现在单页面内完成增删改查功能。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:5pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>2</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）管理分区完成了对分区数据的组合条件查询。使用<span>POI</span>对分区信息导入和导出。导入时采用<span>jQuery</span>的 </span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:5pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span>Ocupload</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">组件完成一件上传，使用<span>Log4j</span>日志技术记录未导入成功的数据和信息，方便工作人员查找。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">3</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">、受理：该模块有业务受理、工单快速录入、工单录入、工单导入、工作单管理五个功能。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">1</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）业务受理功能使用了<span>RMI</span>技术与<span>CRM</span>系统对接，当输入客户地址与数据表分区地址一致时会自动分单，</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">不一致时转入人工分单。当输入客户来电号码时，完成客户信息的自动补全功能。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>2）</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">工单快速录入，使用<span>easyui-datagrid </span>控件实现行编辑效果，进行工作单的快速录入，采用<span>Ajax </span>异步</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">提交方式进行数据保存。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>3）</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">工单录入，通过<span>Struts2</span>的下载功能实现工单模板的下载<span>,</span>通过<span>POI</span>实现大批量的工单导入，使用<span>Log4j</span></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">日志技术记录未导入成功的数据和信息，方便工作人员查找。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">4</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）工作单管理，通过全文检索<span>HibernateSearch</span>和<span>Hibernate</span>二级缓存（<span>ehcache</span>）实现优化。根据到达地</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">点和商品名称进行<span>Lucene</span>全文检索，查询二级缓存，然后获得数据。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">4</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">、调度：该模块有查台转单和人工调度两个功能。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">1</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）查台转单功能，当自动下单成功<span>,</span>但是由于基础信息错误<span>,</span>导致分配的取货人员错误<span>,</span>通过查台转单来解决</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">此类失误。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）在自动下单的时候<span>,</span>由于取件地址无法匹配取件人员<span>,</span>就转入人工调度。手动匹配地址，下单到相应的取</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">件人员。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p style=\"text-indent:-15pt;\">\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>5、</span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">系统管理：该模块有权限管理和用户管理两个功能，权限管理我们采用三张表，分别是权限表、角色表和用 </span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">户表。</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>1</span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\">）表关系：功能点、权限、角色、用户四者多对多关联，所有功能都通过系统管理。其中权限表存放系统 </span>\r\n					</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"color:black;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&