0RVh0U29mdHdhcmUATWljcm9zb2Z0IE9mZmljZX/tNXEAAAA1SURBVCjPY2BgYPgPxc8bGxsZsGEGJEUg7ECMoum4FEkAcQYQ78dlJboOkAYOvIpwOpy+igD2/Gy9V0+YuQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" /></span></span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">项目名称</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">：竞技<span>PK</span>网</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">周期</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">：<span>2012 /06 -- 2013/01 </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">软件开发坏境</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>mysql</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\"><span> </span>+ jdk1.6.0 + </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>eclipse </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">+\r\nmaven</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">开发工具</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>Eclipse +\r\nmysql</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">使用技术</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">Struts2 + Spring3 + Hibernate3.6 (SSH)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">框架<span>+logback+easyUI+freemark+httpclient+</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">FusionCharts</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">项目描述</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">： </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><span>1. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">网站为一款体育竞技平台，目前以足球，篮球为主要导向的平台约战系统。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">2. </span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:9p