an><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">员工留班，兼职员工选择自己上班的时间段。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">营运排班，营运人员如卖品、票务等营运人员的排班、</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">4 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">行政排班，行政人员的排班。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">屏幕管理，对全国万达院线的屏幕进行管理。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">6 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">素材管理，对播放的素材进行管理。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【<b>项目名称</b></span><span>】</span><b><span>新疆农信二代支付系统</span></b></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目周期】<span>2011</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>12</span></span><span>月 </span><span><span>– </span></span><span>至今</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发环境】<span>Weblogic8/Oracle10g/WindowsXp/jdk1.6.0</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发工具】<span>Eclipse</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发技术】<span>java </span></span><span>、</span><span><span>mule</span></span><span>、</span><span><span>smook</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目描述】</span></span></b><span style=\"color:#404040;font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n<span> </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>Account Central System </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>中央银行会计核算数据集中系统，支持支持各项中央银行业务的处理<span>, </span></span><span>是人民银行重要的基础业务和信息系统。系统包含央行会计核算、事后监督、统计分析、会计档案管理、客户对账等功能。业务数据总行集中</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span></span><span>责任描述：</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span></span></span></b><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">负责小额借记来往帐业务的开发</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">负责小额贷记来往帐业务的开发</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">负责实时代收付业务的开发</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">负责一些本地查询业务，如待收付业务 支付登记薄查询业务等的开发</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">兼职助理本项目组数据库的管理</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"><span>例如定期对开发和测试数据库进行<span>backup</span></span><span>和</span><span><span>restore<br />\r\n</span><span> </span></span><span>利用</span><span><span>powerdesigner</span></span><span>工具建立表、索引、外键等数据库对象，</span><span><br />\r\n<span> &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span>生成增量或者全量</span><span><span>sql</span></span><span>脚本，对数据库对象进行升级</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span><span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span>负责开发和修改一些存储过程。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span><span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span>对开发人员提出数据库故障进行诊断排查</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【<b>项目名称</b></span><span>】</span><b><span>中国联通新一代业务支撑系统<span><span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span>（包括</span><span><span>G</span></span><span>网和固网系统）（</span><span><span>BSS4.0</span></span><span>）</span></b></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目周期】<span>2009</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>9</span></span><span>月 </span><span><span>– 2011</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>11</span></span><span>月</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发环境】<span>Weblogic8/Oracle9i/WindowsXp/jdk1.4.2</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发工具】<span>Eclipse</span></span><span>、及</span><span><span>SecureCRT 5.1, ebpm-ide,</span></span><span>等开发工具</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发技术】<span>java </span></span><span>、</span><span><span> tapstry </span></span><span>、</span><span><span> c++</span></span><span>、</span><span><span>JavaScript</span></span><span>以及</span><span><span>js</span></span><span>的</span><span><span>prototype</span></span><span>框架</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目描述】此项目为中国联通新一代业务支撑系统的天津、山西、吉林、内蒙分公司核心版本开发。</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【责任描述】</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>本人负责的部分为该系统（<span>BSS4.0</span></span><span>）营业部分的客户资料综合查询、处理环节查询、积分兑换以、收费功能、号码查询、服务状态查询的开发。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）客户资料综合查询主要包括：客户信息查询，账户信息查询，服务信息查询，优惠信息查询，资源信息查询，邮寄信息查询，历史业务查询，积分信息查询等</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）积分兑换功能包括：积分信息查询，用户兑换信息，积分兑换。当用户有未完工的业务或者积分不足时，不允许进行兑换</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）处理环节查询：可以按照电话号码查询，也可以按照订单号进行查询，查询订单具体走到哪一步。比如是在营业厅还是已经配线配号或者是装机公司。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）收费功能：收费分为在做业务的时候进行收费和直接进入收费界面进行收费，二者是同一个页面。在修改费用或者做业务的时候忘记收费的时候，直接进入收费界面进行收费。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>5</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>）号码查询：根据<span>sim</span></span><span>卡查询电话号码或者根据电话号码查询</span><span><span>sim</span></span><span>卡以及用户姓名等信息</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"><span>服务状态查询：根据网别，客户号码，客户证件号，客户姓名等信息，查询用户所定服务状态的信息。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目名称】河北网通综服系统<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目周期】<span>2008</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>12</span></span><span>月</span><span><span> - 2009</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>9</span></span><span>月</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发环境】</span><span><span>Weblogic8/Oracle9i/WindowsXp/jdk1.4.2</span><span>/unix\r\n/Weblogic</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发工具】<span>java+JavaScript</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发技术】<span>Struts + EJB +\r\noracle + prototype</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目描述】该项目为由河北网通开发的综合服务系统。其中主要负责河北网通的<span>10060</span></span><span>系统和网上营业厅系统。</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【责任描述】</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>本人所负责开发的模块包括：</span><span><br />\r\n<span> 1</span></span><a name=\"undefined\"></a><a name=\"undefined\"></a><span><span>）</span></span><span>客户需求模块。主要功能是记录客户的需求信息，对客户需求信息的审核，对客户需求信息的查询，以及把存在数据库表中关于客户需求信息的数据以</span><span><span>excel</span></span><span>的形式导出。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> 2</span></span><span>）主动营销模块。用户打进电话咨询的同时，座席根据用户情况及目前的一些产品优惠政策、产品信息等为用户做主动营销，并记录营销结果。其中又包括营销信息的记录和营销结果的统计。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> 3</span></span><span>）综合信息查询模块。综合信息查询功能对客户的各种查询请求做出响应，提供给客户相应的信息。我做了其中的障碍查询，以及话费查询。其中障碍查询需要到</span><span><span>112</span></span><span>系统的数据中查询。话费查询是通过</span><span><span>tuxcedo</span></span><span>服务从原有的计费系统查询话费信息，然后把结果返回。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> 4</span></span><span>）障碍回访模块。障碍回访功能是对已经修复的故障电话进行回访，确认修复结果及调查用户的满意度。障碍回访包括人工证实和自动证实。我所做的是人工证实部分。自动证实失败一定次数后，由人工进行证实。支持回访超时限预警、告警功能，通过界面颜色区分。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> 5</span></span><span>）黑名单管理模块。对于那些打恶意骚扰电话的客户，可以把该客户放入黑名单中，在规定的时间内该客户打不进电话。黑名单的有效时间可以选择。在黑名单的有效时间到期后，还可以增加黑名单的有效时间。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目名称】</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>网通渠道管理平台<span>(ERP)</span></span><span>二期</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目周期】<span>2008</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span><span> - 2008</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>12</span></span><span>月</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发环境】</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>Weblogic8/Oracle9i/WindowsXp/jdk1.4.2/unix</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"> /Weblogic</span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发工具】<span>java+JavaScript</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发技术】<span>Struts + EJB + oracle + prototype</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目描述】</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>该项目为网通渠道管理的二期工程，主要对新增的代理类型，供应商，新增业务等进行进一步开发。以及对会员卡的管理和各种统计等</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）代理商基本信息管理：</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对代理商的信息进行维护，内容包括企业名称、地址、法人代表、法人代码、开户银行、银行账号、联系方式、代理业务类型、代理区域、代理商类型、级别、代理商状态、加入时间等等。代理商的编码在整个代理商的生命周期中保持不变，并且保证代理商编码的全局唯一。各地市可以发展自己的理商，省公司可以查询地市各代理商的业务发展情况；代理商支持上下级管理。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> <br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）代理商信息变更管理</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对代理商信息重要数据的新增、变更提供完备维护机制，包括变更者、变更时间、代理商编号、变更项、变更前内容、变更后内容、审核者、审核时间、审核结果等。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）代理商佣金管理</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>主要包括佣金规则管理，佣金的计算以及佣金支付管理。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）库存管理 （包括入库管理，出库管理等）</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>入库管理<span>:</span></span><span>产品入库需要填写入库单据以及单据明细（包括产品名称，库名，库管人员名称等信息）</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">同时信息加入产品信息表。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">出库管理：通过条件查询出要出库的产品，完成出库单据，提交后添加出库信息表，同时修改产品信息表的信息。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）会员卡管理（包括卡设置，售卡等）</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>卡设置：主要是对会员卡的添加等一些基本操作。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"><span>售卡：记录会员卡的销售信息。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目名称】<span>NEC</span></span><span>公司</span><span><span>Hydragui<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目周期】<span>2007</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span><span> - 2008</span></span><span>年</span><span><span>6</span></span><span>月</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发环境】<span>Linux</span></span><span>系统</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发工具】<span>Java+Perl\r\n+Struts<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【开发技术】<span>My eclipse</span></span><span>，</span><span><span>Tomcat</span></span><span>，</span><span><span>Mysql</span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目描述】</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>Hydra</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>是<span>NEC</span></span><span>公司推出的一种硬件的数据备份的系统。</span><span><span>Hydragui</span></span><span>是提供给用户的对</span><span><span>hydra</span></span><span>系统进行控制的一种系统。</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【责任描述】 </span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>本人负责底层的<span>Network</span></span><span>模块的详细设计文档的编写，编码，和</span><span><span>UT</span></span><span>测试。主要功能为：</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span></span><span>① 当系统初装的时候，搜集</span><span><span>hydra</span></span><span>系统网卡的信息，并把信息插入到数据库的 表中。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span></span><span>② 初始化之后，提供给用户接口，让用户可以给网卡设置</span><span><span>IP</span></span><span>地址，子网掩码， 最大传输单元等信息。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span></span><span>③ 对多个网卡做</span><span><span>bond</span></span><span>。让多个物理网卡做成一个逻辑的网卡。可以提高数据的传输速度和确保数据传输的安全。</span><span><br />\r\n<span> </span></span><span>④ 网卡状态监视模块。监视各个网卡的状态，然后按照一定的算法计算出整个网络的状态。并对各个状态用不同的颜色显示</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>【项目名称】勤务管理系统<span><s