left:27.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	u&nbsp;<img width=\"660\" height=\"2\" src=\"file://C:/DOCUME~1/ADMINI~1/LOCALS~1/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.gif\" />业主房源&nbsp;&nbsp; （已上线）\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>开发环境</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SVN、Eclipse、Android ADT、Android 模拟器、Android手机<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>项目描述</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 通过精准的房产信息、深度的行业经验，为用户解决找房过程中遇到的费时费力问题<span>,</span>让找房变得更简单。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:5.25pt;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>主要技术</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	1、UI控件实现界面搭建。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	2、使用ListView展示城市列表以及房屋信息，城市列表的右侧实现一个自定义View A-Z的导航条<span>,</span>方便用户通过点击城市的首字母快速查询并切换城市。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:47.25pt;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;\">\r\n	3、利用MVC模式，实现了项目的的良好架构设计。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	4、使用SlidingMenu实现侧拉菜单。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;\">\r\n	5、远程服务器采用JSON数据格式传输数据，提高数据解析速度。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;\">\r\n	6、使用PopupWindow实现下拉子菜单。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;\">\r\n	7、使用PullRefreshListView实现下拉刷新。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;\">\r\n	8、采用Volley异步获取网络数据，JSON数据解析。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:5.25pt;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>责任描述</b>：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:47.05pt;text-indent:15.85pt;background:white;\">\r\n	负责App界面搭建， BUG调试。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:47.05pt;text-indent:15.85pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	u 西瓜折扣<span>&nbsp; </span>（已上线）<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:6.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>开发环境</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:6.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>SVN、Eclipse、Android ADT、Android 模拟器、Android手机<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:6.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>项目描述</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:15.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 西瓜折扣是国内首个为低价折扣而生的专业App，数千万淘宝买家的共同选择。让你更加省时，省力，省钱。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.05pt;text-indent:2.95pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>主要技术</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:53.7pt;text-indent:9.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	1、使用瀑布流排列商品列表。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:2.0cm;text-indent:6.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	2、使用二级缓存（内存<span>/</span>文件）加载网络图片<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:2.0cm;text-indent:6.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	3、采用FastJson解析JSON网络数据。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:2.0cm;text-indent:6.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	4、使用GridView实现菜单栏显示。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:2.0cm;text-indent:6.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	5、分页实现加载更多。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:2.0cm;text-indent:6.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	6、使用Volley的POST方法向服务器请求注册。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:2.0cm;text-indent:6.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	7、ListView实现意见反馈的显示。<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>责任描述</b>：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>负责App界面搭建与优化，BUG调试。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b>个人项目</b><b> </b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	u<img width=\"660\" height=\"2\" src=\"file://C:/DOCUME~1/ADMINI~1/LOCALS~1/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.gif\" />客户服务平台<span> </span>（已上线）<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:6.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>开发环境</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:6.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>SVN、Eclipse、Android ADT、Android模拟器、Android手机<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:6.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>项目描述</b>：<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:15.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “SOHO客户服务平台”是专门为SOHO业户精心打造的专属App，提供便捷优质的物业服务及SOHO商圈信息服务。主要功能有：通知公告、在线预约及报修、项目介绍、服务流程、SOHO控等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.05pt;text-indent:11.95pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b>主要技术</b>：<span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:51.05pt;text-indent:11.95pt;background:white;\">\r\n	1、采用XUtils获取网络数据，使用FastJson工具类解析Json数据。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	2、SharedPreferences共享参数保存登录信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"ListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	3、采用AutoScrollViewPager实现自动切换图片。\r